cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and language processing. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural machine translation systems. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves the recognition and translation of visual text.
